  "Name": "Floor Openings Needing Handrails",
  "Description": "Two-part QA graph for openings where equipment passes through a floor slab. Part 1 flags equipment with no handrail within a set distance; Part 2 measures the widest plan gap between the opening edge and the equipment (BoundingBox.PlanGap) and tests it against a threshold. Part 1 needs an open model; Part 2 runs on its own.",
